 model comparison for <=3-planet models,\nyet robust planet discoveries require researchers to better understand the\nuncertainty in Z and its connections to model selection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jun 2018 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Oct 2019 00:04:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-04"}
