 the\nbandwidth covered by the ALMA observations is also presented. Because of the\nlimited extent of the emission, firm conclusions about the dynamical evolution\nof the system will have to wait for higher spatial resolution observations.\nHowever, the data presented here support the assumption that the mass-loss rate\nfrom the Mira star strongly varies and is focused on the orbital plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2018 12:29:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-15"}
