ions is possible through manipulation of the depth\nof the lattice, while intrasite correlations are influenced solely by changing\nthe dipolar interaction strength.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2018 14:02:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Jun 2018 07:31:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-09"}
